description.narrative: In 2020, 4,822 parents and caregivers from 75 communities from Ermera and Viqueque municipalities benefitted from parenting education program under a partnership between the Ministry of Social Solidarity and Inclusion and UNICEF Timor-Leste, 44 adolescents led or took part in civic engagement initiatives with UNICEF support, and the capacities of 65 adolescents living in residential care institutions were increased to protect themselves from violence, abuse, neglect and exploitation. | Status:Met | As-of Date:03/02/2021
